<div id="onboarding-step" class="step-fragment">
    <p class="is-uppercase has-text-weight-semibold has-text-grey is-size-7 mb-3">Step {{ currentStepNumber }} of {{ totalSteps }}</p>
    <h2 class="title is-3 mb-3">Set up <span class="brand-word" style="font-size: inherit">Java<span class="brand-runr">Claw</span></span> for real work.</h2>
    <p class="subtitle is-5 has-text-grey-dark">This flow configures your chat provider, stores the required credentials, and lets you edit the workspace instructions that shape assistant behavior.</p>

    <div class="notification is-light content">
        <p class="mb-2"><strong>What happens here:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Select one of the supported providers: Ollama, ChatGPT, or Anthropic.</li>
            <li>Store an API key when the selected provider needs one.</li>
            <li>Edit the workspace AGENT.md file before you start using the app.</li>
            <li>Add the Telegram bot token used by the Telegram integration.</li>
            <li>Mark onboarding complete!</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons mt-4">
        <a class="button is-primary is-medium" href="{{ nextStepUrl }}">Start</a>
        <span class="button is-ghost is-medium htmx-indicator">Loading...</span>
    </div>
</div>